    <text>
        <body>
      
		<pb n="1"/>
			<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>San Francisco</placeName> <date>Dec. 31. 1853</date></p>
			<p><addressee>Mr Isaac Leeser</addressee></p>
          <p rend="indent(2)">Dear Friend</p>
          <p rend="indent(4)">I send you again a few<lb/> subscribers to the &#8220;Occident&#44;&#8221; which I have procured<lb/> since my last&#44; of the <date>15<hi rend="sup">th</hi></date> Inst.</p>
			<p>I also send you 8 copies of the &#8220;Alta California&#8221;&#44; and the &#8220;Whey&#8221;<lb/> which contains several items of Discussion upon the Ob&#45;<lb/>&#45;servance of the <date>Sabbath</date> &#38;c&#44; by the perusal of which&#44; you<lb/> will notice&#44; that we do not allow our Religion to be<lb/> slandered even out here on these <placeName>western Shores</placeName>&#44; &#38; are<lb/> always ready to defend our proud and sacred Faith.<lb/> You&#39;ll read those Articles &#40;I marked them with a black<lb/> rounding&#41; &#38; form then your own Idea about them<lb/> There was nothing else&#44; concerning Jewish Affairs&#44; trans&#45;<lb/>&#45;pired to my knowledge&#59; I shall always endeavor<lb/> to keep you posted up <del>whenever</del> on any thing of any<lb/> Importance to you&#44; what may occur here&#44; &#38; which may serve<lb/> as Interesting News in your Occident.</p>
			<p>The Rainy Season is very severe this year&#44; beyond all<lb/> Expectations&#44; &#38; it is for that Reason&#44; that Merchants<lb/> did fail in laying in sufficient supplies for the<lb/> winter&#44; and the consequence is in some mines&#44; that<lb/> miners have to suffer very much for want of provisions.<lb/> For all other local affairs I refer you to the Papers.</p>
		<pb n="2"/>
			<p>I enjoy&#44; thank God&#44; good Health&#44; hope you may enjoy<lb/> the same Blessing&#59; but Business has moderated greatly&#44; yet<lb/> we console ourselves with bright prospects.</p>
			<p>Let me soon hear from you again.</p>
			<p>Accept the best wishes for your Health &#38; Happiness</p>
          <p rend="indent(1)">from</p>
          <p rend="indent(2)">Yours Truly</p>
          <p rend="indent(4)"><persName role="author">C H Meyers</persName></p>
			<p>N. B. <persName>Mr. Roggenburger</persName> &#38; Family<lb/> desire their kind Regards to you</p>
          
        </body>
    </text>
